{"tid":337314,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"1299 業績等候區","createTime":"2017-07-27T08:03:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T11:00:04.000Z","uid":45440,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aa3e25ef74fec9f0e6d4c8a950a26cdf22f096f0","tid":337314,"uid":45440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:03:32.000Z","msg":"明日要早D起身睇"},{"pid":"ee26677f6863e4f3c9ff94f79765728e015b4364","tid":337314,"uid":17155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:09:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048040362d2a47df038bbce4b939a5f590b1f4ff","tid":337314,"uid":45440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T23:58:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2017/0728/LTN20170728008_C.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkexnews.hk%2Flistedco%2Flistconews%2Fsehk%2F2017%2F0728%2FLTN20170728008_C.pdf&d=ELUN%2FiwwjC2LvQyS5Q5eCP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=8e69792d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2017/0728/LTN20170728008_C.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n出左"},{"pid":"d01889a3363772dc682a696dd9157e48adec29d4","tid":337314,"uid":45440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T23:59:27.000Z","msg":"友邦保險在2017年上半年締造優秀業績<br />\n新業務價值按固定匯率計算增長42%<br />\n營運溢利上升16%─中期股息增加17%<br />\n友邦保險控股有限公司（股份代號：1299）董事會欣然公佈本集團截至2017年5月31日止六個月的未經審核<br />\n綜合業績。按固定匯率基準列示的業績摘要如下：<br />\n新業務價值增長創新高<br />\n&bull; 新業務價值增長42%至17.53億美元<br />\n&bull; 年化新保費上升37%至31.96億美元<br />\n&bull; 新業務價值利潤率增長1.8個百分點至54.2%<br />\n營運溢利創造強勁及回報上升<br />\n&bull; 國際財務報告準則稅後營運溢利上升16%至22.62億美元<br />\n&bull; 國際財務報告準則每股營運盈利增長16%至18.87美仙<br />\n&bull; 內涵價值營運溢利增長21%至34.56億美元<br />\n&bull; 內涵價值營運回報上升至17.1%<br />\n現金流強勁及資本實力雄厚<br />\n&bull; 期內產生的基本自由盈餘增長13%至23.07億美元<br />\n&bull; 自由盈餘為110億美元<br />\n&bull; 內涵價值權益為478億美元；內涵價值為463億美元，於上半年增加42億美元<br />\n&bull; 主要營運公司AIA Co.按香港保險業條例基準計算的償付能力充足率為427%"},{"pid":"ef137ad9143246acebccc379e6432912792f501d","tid":337314,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T00:02:01.000Z","msg":"$70<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdbd0aed58a02f94fb0e9c292e917c2792838672","tid":337314,"uid":41250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T00:16:07.000Z","msg":"Fat fat 了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d38d09d9ce4bab9429644a9181433bcd3c5a8c","tid":337314,"uid":11895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T00:16:31.000Z","msg":"依家好多股業績好都照插"},{"pid":"fa4c14b26d38a1945def98237b88066b7dac1b5e","tid":337314,"uid":5637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T00:19:07.000Z","msg":"預期係幾多？"},{"pid":"30a289d2f33cab706c4e5149b1818f88daf716c9","tid":337314,"uid":121784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T00:22:29.000Z","msg":"第一季整的預測, 推算目標價$六四.八九<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/28/081502_c6dd512358769bd9399df54929713cfa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F28%2F081502_c6dd512358769bd9399df54929713cfa.png&h=dca7f336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日再睇, 跟緊劇本(二)行, 似乎幾準~<br />\n唯一失算係, 內涵價值受惠於美股港股大牛市, 而急升20% (去年好似升得10%)<br />\n所以, 提升目標價至67 (現價$60.7, 市場有理無理炒定先, 所以潛在水位仍然唔夠10%)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/28/081928_7238ebb685313984fe83e051e6f5a35b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F28%2F081928_7238ebb685313984fe83e051e6f5a35b.png&h=21b1bbcc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbc07950d8db847165c9dc92d06e971b12516db0","tid":337314,"uid":105590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28